<plot>The second (and final) episode of an epic about the traditional life in a community of "old believers", who worship an old version of eastern-Orthodox Christianity. Their life is highly regulated by tight rules of behavior and restrictions on personal contacts outside the community. That makes their community almost like a world of it's own. But there is a clash with the real world, and personalities collide too...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?290416</url></doc>
